  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    DocumentMetaDataPipeline
    DocumentMetaDataPipeline runs data through pipeline components to get document meta data like referenceDate, document type[TBD] ...
    FionasMotherEvaluationPipeline
    EvaluationPipeline extends the pipeline by adding a relabel annotator at the beginning and at the end of the pipeline - to transform any annoations from a reference standard into gold labels, and any labels from the pipeline that are being evaluated into copper.
    FionasMotherPipeline
    FionasMother Pipeline is the evolution of Sophia applied to the ciitizen's environment initially.
    FrameworkQuotedSentencePipeline
    FrameworkQuotedSentencePipeline identifies quoted expressions in a document
    FrameworkRMDSentenceNoFilterPipeline

    FrameworkRMDSentencePipeline

    FrameworkSentencePipeline
    FrameworkSentencePipeline chunks documents into utterances via Frameworks annotators It uses the combined framework and ctakes type descriptors.
